<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3151171" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="17"><ahelp hid=".">Adds a text grid to the current page style. This option is only available if Asian language support is enabled under <emph>Language Settings - Languages</emph> in the Options dialog box.</ahelp></paragraph>
